title: Trooper Johnson Fills In For Lunchbox + Amy’s Husband Wants Something Out Of The Bedroom + Mike D Recognized By Famous Country Artist
itunes:title: Trooper Johnson Fills In For Lunchbox + Amy’s Husband Wants Something Out Of The Bedroom + Mike D Recognized By Famous Country Artist
description:
Trooper Chris Johnson with the Governor's Executive Protection Detail filled in for Lunchbox today. He told us about his job as a trooper, his military experience and even answered Bobby’s 'Ask An Officer' questions. Amy tells us about the item(s) her husband wants to remove from their bedroom. Plus, Mike D ran into Brett Eldredge at a local restaurant. Brett recognized him and said hello!
